idered when deploying bat boxes; black boxes are preferable for those bats that use passive rewarming, even in winter when food availability is reduced.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Doty, Anna C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stawski, Clare", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Currie, Shannon E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Geiser, Fritz", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e4f1cdd5ec3af77953ff777907a10903", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/9910c418644c57eedac014385d4e81cda10306b00e8a866062e1296d4819ce2b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/5RSN7RGU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/5RSN7RGU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/738160e6b51c62359bbdf9d7e94aeae6!/b202586-205041", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "162-170", "title": "Journal of Thermal Biology", "volume": "60"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e4f1cdd5ec3af77953ff777907a10903"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:5RSN7RGU"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.jtherbio.2016.07.015"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_t